&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Gelfand, Rennert &amp;amp; Feldman is seeking an Administrative Assistant to join our team of dedicated professionals. The Administrative Assistant is responsible for a variety of administrative tasks to support the operations of the firm&#39;s office and assigned partners.&amp;nbsp;This position is based in-office out of Encino, CA on a full-time basis.&lt;/p&gt;
