&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Establish oneself as a trusted point of contact to employees and the overall business network&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
