&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Maintain electronic and hard copy filing system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Keep the general office area running smoothly by restocking office and kitchen supplies, as needed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Other projects and duties as assigned&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of relative experience within a fully in-office environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma or GED equivalent is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Associate&#39;s degree is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office applications, especially Excel, Word, Outlook, and Teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer service-oriented mentality through active listening and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and time management skills with the ability to multitask&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
